    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/27/125391187/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_2192985960527809766.png",
                "id": "talent28338",
                "key": "轟霆翼斬",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "轟霆翼斬"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>對附屬有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷鳴探知</span>的敵方角色造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>。（如果敵方不存在符合條件角色，則改為對出戰角色造成傷害）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷鳴探知</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此狀態存在期間，可以觸發1次：</span></p><p>所附屬角色到雷音權現及其召喚物造成的傷害+1。</p><p>（同一方場上最多存在一個此狀態。雷音權現的部分技能會以附屬角色為目標。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/27/125391187/8e1f1486bab5fc117e480c06e923634b_7135331635556218270.png",
                "id": "talent25119",
                "key": "雷牆傾軋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷牆傾軋"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">轟雷禁錮</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/27/125391187/71e8c31afa5e7b779c1b2604bccc7b1e_7832787846738338559.png",
                "id": "talent58529",
                "key": "轟雷禁錮",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "轟雷禁錮"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，在敵方場上生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷霆探針</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷霆探針</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>所在陣營角色使用技能後：對所在陣營出戰角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷鳴探知</span>。（每回合1次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷鳴探知</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色受到雷音權現及其召喚物造成的傷害時：</span>移除此狀態，使此傷害+1</p><p>（同一方場上最多存在一個此狀態。雷音權現的部分技能會以附屬角色為目標。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/27/125391187/7fcdf904a4d1623ab0a882884eb4c2e2_1229388530134891950.png",
                "id": "talent42339",
                "key": "雷霆探知",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷霆探知"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>對附屬有雷鳴探知的敵方角色造成造成3點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。（如果敵方不存在符合條件角色，則改為對出戰角色造成傷害）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/27/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7087909487419018541.png",
                "id": "talent10736",
                "key": "轟雷禁錮",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/27/125391187/8fe464d5ca7b4e1ea4b17f6e7f5161fb_613100242752288012.png",
                "title": "轟雷禁錮"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，初始附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">元素生命·雷</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">元素生命·雷</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>角色總是附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>，并且免疫<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/06/125391187/810531dca8fa630e4f5e36322dace05a_6239202586455836430.png",
                "id": "talent60864",
                "key": "元素沉積‧雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "元素沉積‧雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/06/125391187/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_8547517597938885448.png",
                "id": "talent60797",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/06/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3151531335891480128.png",
